Iraqi Child Killed in Mine Explosion
BAGHDAD , December 23 , ( Xinhua ) -- An Iraqi child was killed and two others injured Wednesday in a mine explosion in Iraq 's southern province of al-Muthana , Iraqi News Agency ( INA ) reported .
INA said the mine was one of those dropped by the U.S . - British war planes during the four rounds of bombardments against Iraq before December 19 .
The mine exploded while these children were shepherding their cattle .
The U.S . - British air strikes against Iraq had caused thousands of civilian casualties , said Iraqi officials .
